{
  "stem": "9446.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it began to snow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Poland is not the climate like here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- and they were with dogs, and with bayonets and with rifles pushing us back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They weren't shooting, but they wanted us to go back, not to cross that borderline.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They wouldn't let us inside Russia, which was considered at that time the only way to save our lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] finally, finally, they received some orders to let some of us through.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we found ourselves in the eastern part of Poland, which was kind of occupied by Russian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now what happened-- nobody knew about it-- there was a secret agreement between Hitler, between Germany, and Russia to divide Poland, which is a repetition of the old tradition, so far as Germany's, Russia is concerned.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they divided Poland into a German occupation zone and a Russian occupation zone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we, fortunately, found-- found ourselves then in the part of Poland which is occupied by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a time of Stalin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was bad-- very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nothing compared to, of course, with the situation in Poland occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now being there-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I can't remember all the details.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know that-- yeah, we could not remain there too long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russian, or the communists said that us coming from Warsaw is kind of a suspicious thing for them, because they said we never know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could be a spy for the Nazis, or a spy for the Germans-- you know, nonsense like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was trying to convince them that we are Jewish, and we running away from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why would we-- why would we be spying for the Nazis?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you couldn't convince them of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
